--- .gitignore (原始)
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# Dependencies
.venv/
venv/
node_modules/

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
target/
```

+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Dependencies
.venv/
venv/
env/
.env
.env.local
.env.*

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.swp
*~

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/

# Coverage reports
.coverage
htmlcov/
coverage/

# IDE specific
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Testing
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
```